I feel he's a decent support with alot of utility if used right and is very good if you are confident you can carry the botlane with him, but he can be situational depending on the enemy picks, especially if they have alot of early kill pressure. He's a very aggressive support but he also has good roaming. He's about average as support champions go though unless you have a skill advantage over the enemy team.
